preference.name: AWC_SM_Gantt_Zoom_Level
preference.preference_description: This is a User preference to set the various zoom levels for Gantt. The different possible values are: Day, Week, Month, Year. There is no default value set initially and it loads the view from the unit of time measure value of the schedule.
